        "content": [
            {
                "title": "There's two different ways to make a negative sentence, either using 안 before a verb or conjugating it with -지 않다",
                "details": "1. Putting 안 before a verb makes it negative and doesn't change its tense<br/>2. Conjugating the verb by replacing '다' with '지 않다' makes it negative, this way is also slightly more formal."
